#     Gen X      (44-59) : entries 26-38 (DOB 1966-05-29 -> 1982-05-28)
#     Boomer     (60-77) : entries 39-50 (DOB 1948-05-29 -> 1966-05-28)
#   Income bands:
#     Low (<50K)        : entries 1-8 (mostly Gen Z + early-career)
#     Middle (50K-150K) : entries 9-30 (broad middle)
#     Affluent (>=250K) : entries 31-50 (Wealth Management heavy)
#   Postal code:
#     Entries 1-46 have ZIP. Entries 47-50 have POSTAL_CODE = None.
